# Frontend Rules

- Single-page app; all raid UI in `App.tsx` composition
- Use `useRaidStream` hook for POST + SSE — do not duplicate fetch logic
- API base: `import.meta.env.VITE_API_URL || 'http://localhost:8000'`
- AgentTrace is the autonomy proof panel — always visible during raid
- Disable raid button while `status === 'running'`
- Sponsor badges: Senso Grounded, Gensyn Receipt, ClickHouse stats
